# Curated channels that are NOT reliably present in the upstream source.
# merge_extra.py injects every entry below into dhanytv.m3u on each update so the
# weekly auto-update (which REPLACES dhanytv.m3u with the fresh source) can never
# silently drop them. cleanup_playlist.py dedupes by (tvg-id, url) keeping the
# first occurrence, so the curated copies here win their group.
#
# NOTE: do NOT duplicate channels that already live in the source (e.g. SCTV /
# Indosiar V+). Because dedup keeps the first (top) copy, adding them here would
# RELOCATE them out of "Indonesia Channels" into this group. Keep only channels
# that are either missing from the source or that we genuinely want grouped
# under World Cup.

# <============================================== WorldCup 2026 ===========================================================>

